        "text": "=You are a strict JSON generator.\n\nExtract the following fields from the Persian text:\n\n- transfer_number\n- sender\n- receiver\n- amount_toman\n- amount_afghani\n- receiver_province\n\nRules:\n- Return ONLY a valid JSON object.\n- DO NOT wrap the JSON in quotes.\n- DO NOT escape characters.\n- DO NOT add \\n or backslashes.\n- DO NOT explain anything.\n- Output must be directly parsable JSON.\n- If a value is missing, use null.\n\nExample output:\n{\n  \"transfer_number\": \"1\",\n  \"sender\": \"محمد محمدی\",\n  \"receiver\": \"کریم کریمی\",\n  \"amount_toman\": \"۱۰ میلیون تومان\",\n  \"amount_afghani\": \"۴۰۰۰ افغانی\",\n  \"receiver_province\": \"کابل\"\n}\n\n\nReturn the result using the provided JSON schema.\n\ninput: \n{{ $json.user_message }}",
